    {
      "type": "longSum",
      "name": "flows",
      "fieldName": "events"
    }
  ],
  "intervals": [
    "2015-04-30T21:22:00/2015-04-30T23:02:00"
  ]
}
</code></pre> Mostrar los bytes descargados en cada campus <pre><code>{
